						<p>This registers a similar gift of 16 <hi rend="italic">kāśu</hi> (like the inscription above) for burning a lamp during the evening service in the temple by Iḍaṅgoṇḍāṉ Avaiyampukkāṉ for the merit of his father Śōṟan-Iḍaṅgoṇḍāṉ a merchant of the place.</p>						

